# Pokellection Conventions

Read `AGENTS.md` for the map. These are the non-negotiables.

## Avoid duplication

- Before adding a function, component, or util, search `src/lib`, `src/lib/queries`,
  and `src/components` for an existing one. Extend it; do not recreate it.
- Shared constants/formatters live in `src/lib/utils.ts` (e.g. `formatCad`, `slugify`, `getPhotoUrl`).
- Reusable UI goes in `src/components/`; manager-only UI in `src/components/admin/`.

## Server vs client work

- Mutations from forms → **server actions** (`"use server"`, e.g. `src/app/**/actions.ts`).
- External/long-running or admin operations → **route handlers** under `src/app/api/`.
- Manager-only server actions and routes must call `assertManager(supabase)` first.

## Supabase clients (never construct inline)

```ts
// Server components / actions / routes:
import { createClient } from "@/lib/supabase/server";
// Browser components ("use client"):
import { createClient } from "@/lib/supabase/client";
```

## Definition of done

`npx tsc --noEmit` clean → `npm run build` passes → no duplicated helpers →
regenerate `src/types/supabase.ts` if the schema changed.
